        "created_at": "2022-07-01T02:02:45.990Z",
        "cooked": "<p>We are trying to expose foundationdb as a service to the public internet.</p>\n<p>As I understand foundationdb clients should have cluster file which contains IP and port of coordinators. My question is, does client communicate only with IP addresses in cluster file ?</p>\n<p>More information on client and server communication is appreciated</p>",
